headline: Why Take-Two (TTWO) Shares Are Trading Lower Today
summary: Shares of video game publisher Take Two (NASDAQ:TTWO) fell 3.2% in the morning session after the company announced that the Nintendo Switch 2 port of its game “Borderlands 4” was delayed.
